<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Quiz Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-body h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        .email-body p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .email-body a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100%;
                margin: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>You're Invited to Take a Quiz titled <%= @quiz[:title]%>!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <h2>Hello, <%= @email %>!</h2>
            <p>You just received an invitation from <%= @host.username %> to participate in a quiz created just for you.
            This quiz is designed to test your knowledge and provide valuable feedback.</p>
            <p><strong>Instructions:</strong></p>
            <p>1. Make sure you have a stable internet connection.</p>
            <p>2. Find a quiet place free from distractions.</p>
            <p>3. Allocate sufficient time to complete the quiz without interruptions.</p>
            <p>4. Read each question carefully before answering.</p>
            <p>Click the button below to start the quiz:</p>
            <a href=<%=@url %> target="_blank">Start Quiz</a>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Quiz Builder App. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, contact us at support@quizbuilderapp.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
